{"tid":1405340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚8點出征香討活動 \"2\"","createTime":"2019-08-04T09:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:14:27.000Z","uid":227275,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"958d0e4612d3aedf2b34f0a0f261c12950644930","tid":1405340,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"我知有好多手足唔敢出去前線 <br />\n但係如果上網屌柒藍絲狗就人人都可以做到 而且香討AC又咁易開<br />\n最重要係我地人數多佢地好撚多!<br />\n所以我決定進行長時間既染黃活動!<br />\n將藍色既討論區變做黃色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前高登都可以將混血兒亞歷山大個老母80萬LIKE既PAGE都係洗版洗到收皮 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今次我地唔洗直接同佢地互屌 唔洗同佢地開戰 以防被BAM <br />\n只需要加入大量黃絲討論 例如: 屌尻差佬亂打人 亂拉人 黃絲互相討論差佬有幾仆街<br />\n而且我地將香討染黃 仲可以令班藍絲認清楚事實 變為黃絲 增加己方人數</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n最重要既係搞正負皮系統 屌差佬就正皮 支持差佬就負皮</span></span><br />\n<br />\n事前準備<br />\n1. 開定大量香討AC 防止被BAM<br />\n2. 諗定一堆標題 同黎屌政府同警察<br />\n3. 幫手係連登開POST吹雞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n今晚8點開始行動 <br />\n<br />\n連登出征 寸草不生!</span></span>"},{"pid":"c08caad385d5c9c02f57a6bb0b913e05e94ea721","tid":1405340,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:11:25.000Z","msg":"聽晚8點 連登出征香討大行動!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403200</a><br />\n<br />\n8點開始行動 <br />\n<br />\n連登出征 寸草不生!"},{"pid":"ff95e96e2b7fdc366c83fa5acd5a58b55a92e84c","tid":1405340,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1e378fe3da80bb549126861c7d3db08763ea72d5","tid":1405340,"uid":165598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:12:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6893021240d12be0ac6a26e291e52f3f42816639","tid":1405340,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e378fe3da80bb549126861c7d3db08763ea72d5","tid":1405340,"uid":165598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:12:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/330187956/original.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whicdn.com%2Fimages%2F330187956%2Foriginal.gif&h=048a201d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cec6345d45bce5ea8079230e9524cf11cd342fe4","tid":1405340,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"聽晚8點 連登出征香討大行動!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dvqBrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dvqBrS</a>"}]}